      public Set<ComponentClassMetadata.Qualifier> applicableQualifiers​(Object sceneGraphObject)
      Find the applicable qualifiers in the available qualifiers. A ComponentClassMetadata.Qualifier is applicable if the ComponentClassMetadata.ApplicabilityCheck provided trough Qualifier(URL, String, String, URL, URL, String, ApplicabilityCheck) return true If none were provided during the ComponentClassMetadata.Qualifier instantiation then the ComponentClassMetadata.Qualifier is always applicable
